00:52:13.689 --> 00:52:16.988
[ As Buzz ]
Hiya. fellas! To infinity and beyond!

888
00:52:17.093 --> 00:52:18.856
Hey. look!
It's Buzz!

889
00:52:18.961 --> 00:52:23.398
Hey. Buzz. let's show the guys
our new secret best friends handshake.

890
00:52:23.499 --> 00:52:25.399
Give me five. man!

891
00:52:25.501 --> 00:52:27.332
Something's screwy here.

892
00:52:27.436 --> 00:52:29.927
So you see we're friends now. guys.
Aren't we. Buzz?

893
00:52:30.039 --> 00:52:31.939
[ As Buzz ]
You bet. Give me a hug.

894
00:52:32.041 --> 00:52:34.339
Ho-ho! Boy. I love you too.

895
00:52:34.443 --> 00:52:36.343
See? It is Buzz.

896
00:52:36.445 --> 00:52:39.039
- Now give back the lights. Potato Head.
- Wait just a minute.

897
00:52:39.148 --> 00:52:42.515
- What are you tryin' to pull?
- Nothing!
- [ Screaming ]

898
00:52:42.618 --> 00:52:45.985
- [Group Murmuring]
- [ Grunts. Retches ]

899
00:52:46.088 --> 00:52:47.988
- Oh. that is disgusting.
- Murderer!

900
00:52:48.090 --> 00:52:50.354
- No! No. no. no. no. no!
- You murdering dog!

901
00:52:50.459 --> 00:52:52.893
- It's not what you think. I swear!
- Save it for the jury.

902
00:52:52.995 --> 00:52:54.986
I hope Sid pulls
yourvoice box out. ya creep.

903
00:52:55.097 --> 00:52:57.497
No. no! No. no!
Don't leave! Don't leave!

904
00:52:57.600 --> 00:53:00.068
Ya gotta help us. please! You don't
know what it's like over here!

905
00:53:00.169 --> 00:53:02.069
Come on.
Let's get outta here.

906
00:53:02.171 --> 00:53:04.639
Go back to your lives. citizens.
Show's over.

907
00:53:04.740 --> 00:53:06.765
[Woody]
Come back!Slink!

908
00:53:06.876 --> 00:53:11.176
Slink! Please!
Please! Listen to me!

909
00:53:11.280 --> 00:53:14.340
No! No! Come back!

910
00:53:14.450 --> 00:53:17.248
Slinky!

911
00:53:17.486 --> 00:53:19.545
[Thunder Rumbling]

912
00:53:21.958 --> 00:53:25.553
[ Thumping. Clattering]

913
00:53:25.661 --> 00:53:28.357
Buzz! Go away!

914
00:53:28.464 --> 00:53:31.433
You disgusting freaks!
Aaah!

915
00:53:31.534 --> 00:53:35.231
All right. back!
Back. you cannibals! Aah! Oof!.

916
00:53:38.307 --> 00:53:42.266
He is still alive. andyou're
not gonna get him. you monsters!

917
00:53:42.378 --> 00:53:44.312
What are you doin'?

918
00:53:46.682 --> 00:53:48.912
Hey. Hey. they fixed you.

919
00:53:52.188 --> 00:53:54.247
But-- But they're cannibals.

920
00:53:54.357 --> 00:53:58.123
We saw them eat
those other toys.

921
00:54:01.731 --> 00:54:03.631
[ Quacks ]

922
00:54:04.934 --> 00:54:07.494
Uh. sorry. I-I-I thought
that you were gonna--

923
00:54:07.603 --> 00:54:10.094
[ Chuckles ]
You know. you know. eat my friend.

924
00:54:10.206 --> 00:54:12.174
[Woody]
Hey. no. no. wait. hey!

925
00:54:12.274 --> 00:54:14.105
- What's wrong?
- [Sid's Mom ] Sid?

926
00:54:14.210 --> 00:54:15.472
[Sid]
Not now. Mom! I'm busy!

927
00:54:15.578 --> 00:54:18.479
- Sid! Buzz. come on!
-[Mom ] You left that door open.

928
00:54:18.581 --> 00:54:23.484
Get up! Use your legs! Fine!
Let Sid trash you. but don't blame me!

929
00:54:24.620 --> 00:54:27.851
It came!
It finally came!

930
00:54:27.957 --> 00:54:31.085
Ha. ha!

931
00:54:31.193 --> 00:54:33.093
"The Big One."

932
00:54:36.232 --> 00:54:38.257
" Extremely dangerous.

933
00:54:38.367 --> 00:54:40.995
Keep out ofreach ofchildren. "

934
00:54:42.638 --> 00:54:46.130
Cool!
What am I gonna blow?

935
00:54:46.242 --> 00:54:49.143
Man. Hey. where's
that wimpy cowboy doll?

936
00:54:59.288 --> 00:55:01.256
[Buzz Buzzing]

937
00:55:03.059 --> 00:55:07.962
Yes. I've always wanted
to put a spaceman into orbit.

938
00:55:14.937 --> 00:55:16.700
-[Tape Peeling]
- [Sid] Heh. heh.

939
00:55:16.806 --> 00:55:20.640
Now. Yes.

940
00:55:20.743 --> 00:55:22.472
[Sinister Chuckle ]

941
00:55:23.813 --> 00:55:26.873
-[Thunderclap ]
- Oh. no!

942
00:55:26.982 --> 00:55:29.075
[ Thunder Rumbling]

943
00:55:29.185 --> 00:55:31.312
Oh. man!

944
00:55:36.859 --> 00:55:38.759
Sid Phillips reporting.

945
00:55:38.861 --> 00:55:40.954
Launch of the shuttle
has been delayed...

946
00:55:41.063 --> 00:55:43.861
due to adverse weather
conditions at the launch site.

947
00:55:43.966 --> 00:55:47.060
Tomorrow's forecast: sunny.

948
00:55:47.169 --> 00:55:51.037
