but all I could find was your hat.

951
00:55:59.014 --> 00:56:01.073
But what if we
leave them behi nd?

952
00:56:01.183 --> 00:56:06.246
Oh. don't worry. honey.
I 'm sure we'll find Woody
and Buzz before we leave tomorrow.

953
00:56:10.726 --> 00:56:13.695
