I'm sorry. It's just that I get--
I get so nervous before I travel.

957
00:56:21.937 --> 00:56:24.405
How did I get stuck
with you as a moving buddy?

958
00:56:24.507 --> 00:56:27.305
Everyone else was picked.

959
00:56:29.145 --> 00:56:32.239
[ Snoring ]

960
00:56:32.348 --> 00:56:34.248
