Oh. Woody.

961
00:56:34.350 --> 00:56:39.447
If onlyyou could see
how much Andy misses you.

962
00:56:42.258 --> 00:56:44.818
[Thunder Rumbling]

963
00:56:44.927 --> 00:56:48.328
[ Snoring ]

964
00:56:48.430 --> 00:56:51.763
[ Straining ]

965
00:56:51.867 --> 00:56:54.859
Psst. Psst! Hey. Buzz!

966
00:56:59.775 --> 00:57:02.266
Hey.

967
00:57:02.378 --> 00:57:07.483
Get over here andsee if
you can get this toolbox offme.

968
00:57:07.550 --> 00:57:11.111
Oh. come on. Buzz. I--

969
00:57:11.220 --> 00:57:15.486
Buzz. I can't do this without you.
I need your help.

970
00:57:15.591 --> 00:57:19.960
I can't help.
I can't help anyone.

971
00:57:20.062 --> 00:57:23.293
Why. sureyou can. Buzz.
You can get me outta here.

972
00:57:23.399 --> 00:57:26.300
Then I'll get that rocket offyou.
and we'll make a break for Andy's house.

973
00:57:26.402 --> 00:57:29.667
Andy's house. Sid's house.
What's the difference?

974
00:57:29.772 --> 00:57:34.038
Oh. Buzz. You've had a big fall.
You must not be thinking clearly.

975
00:57:34.143 --> 00:57:37.408
No. Woody. For the first time
I am thinking clearly.

976
00:57:37.513 --> 00:57:41.108
You were right all along.
I'm not a Space Ranger.

977
00:57:41.217 --> 00:57:44.983
I'm just a toy. a stupid.
little. insignificant toy.

978
00:57:45.087 --> 00:57:46.987
Whoa. hey. wait a minute.

979
00:57:47.089 --> 00:57:49.819
Bein' a toy is a lot better
than bein' a. a Space Ranger.

980
00:57:49.925 --> 00:57:51.859
- Yeah. right.
- No. it is.

981
00:57:51.961 --> 00:57:54.862
Look. over in that house is a kid
who thinks you are the greatest.

982
00:57:54.964 --> 00:57:58.161
Andit's not because
you're a Space Ranger. pal.

983
00:57:58.267 --> 00:58:02.033
It's becauseyou're a toy.
You are his toy.

984
00:58:02.137 --> 00:58:04.196
But why would Andy want me?

985
00:58:04.306 --> 00:58:08.709
Why would Andy want you? Look at you!
You're a Buzz Lightyear.

986
00:58:08.811 --> 00:58:11.837
Any other toy would give up
his moving partsjust to beyou.

987
00:58:11.947 --> 00:58:15.576
You've got wings.
You glow in the dark. You talk!

988
00:58:15.684 --> 00:58:18.949
Your helmet does
that. that. that whoosh thing.

989
00:58:19.054 --> 00:58:23.388
You are a cool toy.

990
00:58:25.661 --> 00:58:29.062
As a matter of fact.
you're too cool.

991
00:58:29.164 --> 00:58:32.361
I mean. I mean. what chance
does a toy like me have...

992
00:58:32.468 --> 00:58:35.699
against a Buzz Lightyear
action figure?

993
00:58:35.804 --> 00:58:38.398
All I can do is--

994
00:58:38.507 --> 00:58:42.910
[ Voice Box ]
There's a snake in my boots.

995
00:58:43.012 --> 00:58:44.980
Whywould Andy everwant
to playwith me...

996
00:58:45.080 --> 00:58:47.947
when he's gotyou?

997
00:58:48.050 --> 00:58:52.612
I'm the one that should be
strapped to that rocket.

998
00:59:00.796 --> 00:59:03.629
[Birds Chirping]

999
00:59:15.177 --> 00:59:18.476
Listen. Buzz.
forget about me.

1000
00:59:18.580 --> 00:59:21.481
You should get outta here
while you can.

1001
00:59:21.583 --> 00:59:23.983
