1002
00:59:25.721 --> 00:59:28.918
[ Sighs ]

1003
00:59:30.025 --> 00:59:32.050
[ Clattering]

1004
00:59:32.161 --> 00:59:34.629
Buzz? What are you doin'?
I thought you were--

1005
00:59:34.730 --> 00:59:37.722
Come on. Sheriff. There's a kid
over in that house who needs us.

1006
00:59:37.833 --> 00:59:39.733
Now let's get you out of this thing.
[ Grunts ]

1007
00:59:39.835 --> 00:59:41.962
Yes. sir!

1008
00:59:42.071 --> 00:59:45.837
- [ Straining ]
- Come on. Buzz. We can do it.

1009
00:59:45.941 --> 00:59:49.843
- [ Grunts ]
-[EngineApproaching]

1010
00:59:51.613 --> 00:59:53.513
Woody. it's the moving van.

1011
00:59:53.615 --> 00:59:56.345
We gotta get outta here now.

1012
00:59:56.452 --> 00:59:58.352
[ Grunts ]

1013
01:00:00.622 --> 01:00:03.113
Come on. Buzz.

1014
01:00:04.293 --> 01:00:07.023
All right.
[ Grunts ] Buzz!

1015
01:00:07.129 --> 01:00:09.859
- Hey. I'm out!
- Almost there.

1016
01:00:13.702 --> 01:00:17.365
[ Sputters ]
I want to ride the pony. [ Snores ]

1017
01:00:17.473 --> 01:00:21.603
Phew. Woody?

1018
01:00:21.710 --> 01:00:25.271
Woody? Are you all right?

1019
01:00:25.381 --> 01:00:27.941
I'm fine. I'm okay.

1020
01:00:28.050 --> 01:00:30.314
[ Ringing ]

1021
01:00:30.419 --> 01:00:33.183
[ Ringing Continues ]

1022
01:00:33.288 --> 01:00:36.553
[Ringing Continues ]

1023
