Ringing Stops ]

1024
01:00:38.727 --> 01:00:42.857
Oh. yeah!
Time for liftoff!. Whoo!

1025
01:00:44.900 --> 01:00:47.562
To infinity and beyond!

1026
01:00:47.669 --> 01:00:49.569
Whoo-hoo!

1027
01:00:53.575 --> 01:00:56.567
[ Growls. Barks.
Snarling ]

1028
01:00:56.678 --> 01:00:59.476
- Aah! Back. back.
- [ Barks. Yelps ]

1029
01:00:59.581 --> 01:01:01.776
- Down. down!
- [Barks ]

1030
01:01:01.884 --> 01:01:06.048
- Okay. what do I do?
Come on. Woody. Think.
-[ Toys Clattering]

1031
01:01:07.322 --> 01:01:09.688
Guys!

1032
01:01:09.792 --> 01:01:12.488
No. no. no. no! Wait!
Wait. Listen. please.

1033
01:01:12.594 --> 01:01:16.655
There's a good toy down there. and he's
gonna be blown to bits in a few minutes.

1034
01:01:16.765 --> 01:01:20.223
All because of me.
We've gotta save him.

1035
01:01:20.335 --> 01:01:23.236
And. uh--
But I need your help.

1036
01:01:25.974 --> 01:01:27.737
[Toy Creaking]

1037
01:01:30.112 --> 01:01:34.572
Please. He's my friend.

1038
01:01:34.683 --> 01:01:37.243
And he's the only one
I've got.

1039
01:01:39.288 --> 01:01:43.349
[ Tapping Morse Code ]

1040
01:01:43.459 --> 01:01:45.586
-[Toy Trumpeting]
-[Tapping Continues ]

1041
01:01:48.864 --> 01:01:53.426
Thankyou.
Okay. I think I know what to do.

1042
01:01:53.535 --> 01:01:56.026
We're gonna have
to break a few rules.

1043
01:01:56.138 --> 01:01:59.232
But if it works.
it'll help everybody.

1044
01:02:06.048 --> 01:02:08.710
[ Sighs ]

1045
01:02:08.817 --> 01:02:12.776
-[Pounding]
- [Sid] Houston to Mission Control.
Come in. Control.

1046
01:02:12.888 --> 01:02:17.450
Launch pad is
being constructed.

1047
01:02:17.559 --> 01:02:18.992
- [ Growls ]
-[ Woody]All right. listen up.

1048
01:02:19.094 --> 01:02:21.961
I need Pump Boy here.
Ducky here.

1049
01:02:22.064 --> 01:02:25.830
- Legs. you're with Ducky.
- [ Quacks ]

1050
01:02:25.934 --> 01:02:28.129
RollerBob and I don't move
till we get the signal. Clear?

1051
01:02:28.237 --> 01:02:31.729
- [ Quacks ]
- Okay. Let's move!

1052
01:02:33.475 --> 01:02:34.567
[ Barks ]

1053
01:02:38.080 --> 01:02:40.844
[Barking Continues ]

1054
01:02:48.524 --> 01:02:50.822
[ Quacks ]

1055
01:02:52.094 --> 01:02:53.994
Wind the frog.

1056
01:03:00.769 --> 01:03:03.329
- ** [ " Pop Goes the Weasel" ]
-[Dog Snarls ]

1057
01:03:03.438 --> 01:03:06.999
- [ Chitters ]
-[Frog Revs ]

1058
01:03:07.109 --> 01:03:10.010
[ Straining ]

1059
01:03:12.848 --> 01:03:15.942
[Birds Chirping]

1060
01:03:16.051 --> 01:03:18.212
- Wait for the signal.
-[Frog Revs ]

1061
01:03:22.291 --> 01:03:25.226
[ Quacks. Mutters ]

1062
01:03:25.327 --> 01:03:28.057
[ Muttering ]

1063
01:03:30.399 --> 01:03:32.333
[ Blubbers ]

1064
01:03:32.434 --> 01:03:35.028
- [ Ringing ]
- Go!

1065
01:03:35.137 --> 01:03:36.798
- [ Growls ]
- [ Engine Revving ]

1066
01:03:36.905 --> 01:03:40.466
- [ Barks ]
- All right. let's go!

1067
01:03:40.576 --> 01:03:42.567
[Hannah ]
I'll get it!

1068
01:03:42.678 --> 01:03:44.976
Now!

1069
01:03:45.080 --> 01:03:46.377
- I'm coming. I'm coming.
-[Ringing Continues ]

1070
01:03:46.481 --> 01:03:49.575
- [ Quacks ]
-[Barking Continues ]

1071
01:03:49.685 --> 01:03:51.880
[ Barking ]

1072
01:03:55.724 --> 01:03:57.658
- [ Yelps ]
- Scud!

1073
01:03:57.759 --> 01:04:01.217
- [ Laughing ]
- [ Snarls ]

1074
01:04:01.330 --> 01:04:03.855
- [ Barks ]
- Stupid dog.

1075
01:04:03.966 --> 01:04:06.958
[Barking Continues ]

1076
01:04:09.771 --> 01:04:11.864
Lean back!

1077
01:04:16.644 --> 01:04:21.707
[Sid] Uh. Mission Control. is
the launch pad construction complete?

1078
01:04:21.815 --> 01:04:24.409
Uh. roger. Rocket is now
secured to guide wire.

1079
01:04:24.518 --> 01:04:27.681
We are currently obtaining
the ignition sticks.

1080
01:04:27.788 --> 01:04:31.554
- Countdown will commence
momentarily. Stand by.
- Let's go.

1081
01:04:31.659 --> 01:04:36.062
Hey. Ma! Where are the matches?
Oh. wait. Here they are. Never mind.

1082
01:04:36.163 --> 01:04:38.723
- Woody! Great!
Hel p me outta this thing.
- Shh!

1083
01:04:38.832 --> 01:04:41.232
- What?
- It's okay.

1084
01:04:41.335 --> 01:04:43.895
Everything's under control.

1085
01:04:44.004 --> 01:04:46.097
- [ Whispering ]
Woody. what are you doing?
- Houston.

1086
01:04:46.206 --> 01:04:50.643
All systems are go.
Requesting permission to launch--

1087
01:04:50.744 --> 01:04:54.771
Hey? How'd you get out here?

1088
01:04:54.882 --> 01:04:58.374
Oh. well. You and I
can have a cookout later.

1089
01:04:58.485 --> 01:05:01.045
[ Chuckles ]

1090
01:05:01.155 --> 01:05:03.817
Houston. do we have
permission to launch?

1091
01:05:03.924 --> 01:05:05.983
[ Imitating Radio Static ]
Uh. roger. Permission granted.

1092
01:05:06.093 --> 01:05:09.756
You are confirmed
at "T"minus ten seconds.

1093
01:05:10.864 --> 01:05:14.561
And counting.
Ten. nine.

1094
01:05:14.668 --> 01:05:17.330
eight. seven. six.

1095
01:05:17.438 --> 01:05:20.305
five. four. three. two.

1096
01:05:20.407 --> 01:05:25.003
- one!
-[ Woody's Voice Box ]
Reach for the sky!

1097
01:05:25.112 --> 01:05:28.604
- Huh?
- This town ain't big enough
for the two of us.

1098
01:05:28.716 --> 01:05:33.744
- What?
