1103
01:05:49.303 --> 01:05:51.635
That's right!
Yourtoys!

1104
01:05:51.739 --> 01:05:54.037
Mama!

1105
01:05:54.141 --> 01:05:56.336
Mama!

1106
01:05:56.443 --> 01:06:00.004
Mama! Mama!

1107
01:06:03.784 --> 01:06:05.979
[ Gasps ]

1108
01:06:07.655 --> 01:06:09.885
[ Squeaks ]

1109
01:06:09.990 --> 01:06:12.185
[ Gasps ]

1110
01:06:15.996 --> 01:06:18.157
Aaah!
[ Gasps ]

1111
01:06:18.265 --> 01:06:20.165
Aaah!

1112
01:06:20.267 --> 01:06:22.633
- [ Gasps ]
- Mama!

1113
01:06:22.736 --> 01:06:28.197
From now on. you must take
good care ofyour toys!

1114
01:06:28.308 --> 01:06:32.472
Because ifyou don't.
we'll find out. Sid.

1115
01:06:32.579 --> 01:06:38.211
