everything.

1116
01:06:39.653 --> 01:06:42.019
So play nice.

1117
01:06:42.122 --> 01:06:45.922
Aaah!

1118
01:06:47.795 --> 01:06:52.061
Ha-ha! We did it!
We did it! Ha-ha! Yes!

1119
01:06:52.166 --> 01:06:54.930
The toys!
The toys are alive!

1120
01:06:55.035 --> 01:06:58.869
N-Nice toy.
Aaah!

1121
01:06:58.972 --> 01:07:01.998
- [ Whimpers ]
- What's wrong. Sid?

1122
01:07:02.109 --> 01:07:04.771
